snippet.textDisplay: Bruh wdym the SE 2 is a disappointment.  I know it’s not what people were expecting but it literally took Apple 3 damn years just to remove a stupid notch from their FLAGSHIP phone (according to the leaks).  Like, dude, if anything you’re getting an upgraded (albeit very little) iPhone 8 for cheaper AND longer software support.  The supposed iPhone twelve just seems like a disappointing iPhone eleven without a notch which took wayyyyyyy too long to get rid of.  On top of that, the alleged in screen fingerprint sensor was done by tons of brands by now.  I lost faith in Apple a long time ago, and the usual new leaks don’t change my opinion.  I’m just glad that they gave the extremely budget friendly (in their eyes) IPhone SE another chance.
